WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:44.000
 Remove bolts. 

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:48.000
 Remove the brake caliper from the brake disc. 

00:00:49.000 --> 00:01:08.000
 Disassemble the clip and then pull the pin out. 

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:19.000
 Disassemble the brake pads. 

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:38.000
 Install new brake pads. 

00:01:38.000 --> 00:02:06.000
 Mount pin and then the clip. 

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:15.000
 Mount the caliper on the brake disc. 

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:47.000
 Fit bolts. 

